 sou anebhsan eiv mnhmosunon enwpion tou yeou.
10:5 kai nun pemqon eiv iopphn andrav kai metapemqai simwna
 ton epikaloumenon petron:
10:6 outov xenizetai para tini simwni bursei, w estin oikia
 para yalassan.
10:7 wv de aphlyen o aggelov o lalwn tw kornhliw, fwnhsav
 duo twn oiketwn autou kai stratiwthn eusebh twn proskarterountwn
